# Bini Terminal ASCII Player

Play videos and images as full screen color ASCII art directly in your terminal!

## Installation

```bash
pip install bini-terminal-ascii-player
```

## Usage

### Play a video:
```bash
tmp play video.mp4
```

### Play an image:
```bash
tmp play image.jpg
```

### Show animated parrot (like curl parrot.live):
```bash
tmp parrot
```

### Get help:
```bash
tmp --help
```

