## Controls During Playback

- `Q` - Quit
- `F` - Toggle info display
- `P` - Pause

## Supported Formats

- **Video**: MP4, AVI, MOV, MKV, WMV, FLV
- **Image**: JPG, JPEG, PNG, BMP, GIF

## Requirements

- Python 3.7+
- OpenCV
- Pillow
- NumPy

